[[File:John Livingstone-Learmonth.jpg|right|thumb|John Livingstone - Learmonth in the Rhone]]
'''John Livingstone-Learmonth'''  is a [[United Kingdom|British]] [[wine]] writer. He has published four books on [[Rhône wine]]s<ref>[http://www.thewinedoctor.com/otherresources/livingstonelearmonth.shtml Wine Books: John Livingstone-Learmonth], Wine Doctor, accessed 2010-09-09</ref> and has consulted on books such as the 'World Atlas of Wine' by [[Jancis Robinson]] and [[Hugh Johnson (wine)|Hugh Johnson]].

